{"tid":1765319,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)明日傳奇 第1-4季","createTime":"2019-12-01T18:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T16:58:22.000Z","uid":29160,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"67d5ec499a92f22f35dccbd86d007fb76cc351fc","tid":1765319,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:33:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啊~~~死黑警~~~又唔做嘢又唔讀書</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0a0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=ed610181\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0a0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=7b5e4c18\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0a0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=16655785\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://godhatesgeeks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/LoT-Feature.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgodhatesgeeks.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F01%2FLoT-Feature.png&h=0883962a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Cs1qeiMVUAAMK-N.png:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCs1qeiMVUAAMK-N.png%3Alarge&h=e6451025&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/images/video_poster/2018/2018100310015320807d73d8dbf19dc4fc3188a56928524018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fvideo_poster%2F2018%2F2018100310015320807d73d8dbf19dc4fc3188a56928524018.jpg&h=5c1d327a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.2166年，全球都被汪達爾&middot;薩維奇（加斯帕&middot;科倫普飾）所征服。在薩維奇殺死時間大師里普&middot;亨特（阿瑟&middot;達維爾飾）的妻子後，里普&middot;亨特便請求時間大師們准許他集結一支隊伍，趕在薩維奇毀掉未來前阻止他。之後回到了2016年，里普&middot;亨特找了火風暴、原子俠、白金絲雀、冷凍隊長等人組成團隊，登上了里普的飛船&quot;乘波號&quot;，穿越回到1975年去阻止薩維奇&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.由於時間領主總部摧毀，傳奇們被迫擔負起修復歷史的使命。然而他們也擔心時俠的警告，傳奇們發現Damien Darhk於1942年的時候企圖發射核武炸毀紐約。<br />\n而Damien Darhk更與逆閃電及黑箭等組成「末日軍團」。逆閃電協助末日軍團的目的就是要防止神速力怪物的追捕<br />\n<br />\n3.在2017年洛杉磯看到時間大亂的傳奇團隊，最後發現原來已經離開的Rip Hunter成立了時間管理局替代時間領主。原來在他離開後發覺他們打亂了時間，於是就成立了時間管理局來解決事件。在2017年，時間管理局規模已經十分宏大。<br />\n同時，Rip Hunter也宣布傳奇解散。Sara回到星城，並在一間衛浴店超市里工作。火風暴、鋼鐵隊長則回到中城，鋼鐵隊長成為了該地排第二的超級英雄。而火風暴的兩人則繼續他們的生活。Jax繼續進修大學，而Martin則與他因修復時間而產生的副作用&mdash;&mdash;他的女兒Lily等共享天倫。Ray則在矽谷工作。Amaya則回到1942年她的小山村。Mick Rory則在阿魯巴度假<br />\n<br />\n4.五個月後，傳奇解決了所有時間錯誤。但時間線外的魔法生物開始出現影響時間線，魔法顧問康斯坦汀：驅魔神探及變形怪Charlie加入了傳奇小隊。另一方面，時間管理局為因應魔法生物的出現也開始建立防範機制，Nate為了逃避情傷也加入了時間管理局與Ave共事。 <br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0a0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=08b04c8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0a0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=be893630\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8a55d94f7772c7cc9f899df29b71344bf72d52","tid":1765319,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T18:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b3ee877ee9461073f6067362bae14972b51fcd","tid":1765319,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T19:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a0ad80e7a525a3134865945cd483128338b879","tid":1765319,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d1b8a238a21d05797f0a3ae18bb80b973b2cb0","tid":1765319,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e516db93e590458be3754393026760f05987c86f","tid":1765319,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afaefa2c0e0597fe3b1f6db69337d96eaa4daeb5","tid":1765319,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T19:11:25.000Z","msg":"<im